### Welcome to Privacy Strike Inc. web site!
Our company is engaged in development of various solutions, focused on privacy.
### Our goals
Our main task is the development and maintenance of means to ensure privacy.
### Why privacy is so serious?
Good question. Privacy required everyone, without exception, for to be informed with life.
### What to do?
You can use our set of filters for [Adblock Plus](https://adblockplus.org), [TPB](https://github.com/privacystrike/TPB), that blocks all third-party components on the Web.
### Where I can get it?
Just click  right now!
